web.controller.communication.opcua

Class NodeManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.services.NodeManagementServices
      • web.controller.communication.opcua.NodeManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebCommunication, org.eclipse.milo.opcua.stack.core.application.services.NodeManagementServiceSet

    public class NodeManager
extends org.eclipse.milo.opcua.sdk.server.services.NodeManagementServices
implements WebCommunication
    This class is a change class from the Milo example. In this class the create and delete operations from clients are forwarded to the Reprsentation Manager and the answers are converted to OPC UA answers.
